<section class="features horizontal">
    <div class="container border-top">
        
        <div class="text-center">
            <h2>Choose When You Transport Your Car</h2>
            <p class="lead text-muted">Safe, secure, and expedited auto transport â€” move when you choose!</p>
        </div>
            
        <div class="feature">
            <i class="icon icon-map-pin icon-box gradient-blue"></i>
            <p>Auto transport requires the coordination of several factors, making timeliness and flexibility necessary components. With Expedited Transport, you can feel at ease and <strong>have your car picked up on the exact date of your move.</strong></p>
            <p>Making a last minute decision?  With Expedited Car Shipping, you can get your car transported as soon as 24-48 hours after ordering.</p>
            <p>The premium paid for this service is a small price to pay for the added convenience and satisfaction that comes along with express shipping. The transporter will be rearranging his or her route to accommodate your time-sensitive pickup.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
        
        
        
        
<section class="factors">
