            <div class="col-sm-4">
                <div class="box shipping-cost">
                    <h4>Shipping Cost</h4>
                    <p>Price depends on several factors including: seasonal supply and demand, flexibility of dates, car type, car condition, location, distance, and transport type (open or enclosed car transport).</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            
            <div class="col-sm-4">
                <div class="box extra-care">
                    <h4>Priority Care</h4>
                    <p>By choosing expedited shipping, you are accelerating the car transportation process. Car carriers will consider the delivery of your vehicle as a top priority and make necessary accommodations.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            
            <div class="col-sm-4">
                <div class="box restrictions">
                    <h4>Limitations and Extras</h4>
                    <p>Remote or rural pickup often requires the extra services of a local towing company. This method is used as a last resort, because it may lead to prolonged delivery times. Please ask one of our agents if you think this limitation may apply to you.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        
